Class Voucher

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.edgrantJBusRD.dbjson.Serializable
      • com.edgrantJBusRD.Voucher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Serializable>
    public class Voucher
extends Serializable
    The Voucher class represents a voucher that can be applied to a price. This class extends the Serializable class to support serialization.
